  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "synopsis",
      "abstract": "This House Joint Resolution establishes the Delaware Task Force on Procurement and Contracting Modernization. It also requires the Task Force to submit a report by September 30, 2027, with its findings and recommendations and any recommended legislation to improve Delaware\u2019s procurement, grantmaking, and contracting practices."
